title: Episode 34 w/ Dame Dash
itunes:title: Episode 34 w/ Dame Dash
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys drink it up with hip hop mogul Dame Dash. The guys discuss N.O.R.E. and Dame Dash's long history of working together through music and films, and working together in the future. Dame also discusses his current projects and his feelings about stepping away from the music industry. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
